                            description="&lt;h3>Fixed Deposit in Foreign Currency (FCNR)&lt;/h3>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>Invest in USD, GBP, SGD, CAD, or AUD with no tax on interest earned in India.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>&lt;p>Principal and interest are fully repatriable.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>&lt;p>Flexible tenure for USD (1-5 years), and GBP, CAD, AUD, and SGD (1- Less than 3 Years).&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>&lt;p>85% overdraft in INR against FCNR deposits (up to ₹5 Crores)&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>Minimum deposit:&lt;ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>USD &amp;amp; GBP: 1,000&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>SGD, CAD, AUD: 2,000&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;"
